Class Stream

  • java.lang.Object
    • Stream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Stream
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    A class representing a stream. Contains a set of species along with flow rates, temperature, and pressure.
